Package org.beansinc.bobsled_jousting

Class TeamMember<A extends Enum<A>,M extends Enum<M>>

java.lang.Object
org.beansinc.bobsled_jousting.TeamMember<A,M>
Type Parameters:
A - the generic type of attributes (Must be an enummerator)
M - the generic type of modifiers (Must be an enummerator)
Direct Known Subclasses:
Contestant, Sled
public class TeamMember<A extends Enum<A>,M extends Enum<M>> extends Object
Provides the basic functionality for all team members (Sleds and Contestants). Has generic types so different attributes and modifiers can be given to a team member

      Instantiates a new team member.
      Parameters:
      name - the team member's name
      attributes - custom attributes to be instaniated, this one is already in a map, and does not need to be converted
      modifiers - custom modifiers to be instaniated, this one is already in a set, and does not need to be converted
      value - the funds value of the team member
